OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter some early brightness in
OL,6,Fthe east, rain will move slowly
OL,7,Fsoutheastwards across Scotland and
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland. Some showery rain
OL,9,Fdeveloping across west Wales and the
OL,10,Fwest of England. Elsewhere, early mist
OL,11,Fclearing to a very mild, mostly sunny
OL,12,Fday.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FRain, with hill snow in the
OL,15,Fnorth, continuing southeastwards
OL,16,Facross the north and west of England
OL,17,Fand Wales. Dry with low cloud to the
OL,18,Fsoutheast. Clearer with frost further
OL,19,Fnorthwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
