OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FRain will edge southeastwards
OL,6,Facross England and Wales. Scotland and
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland look largely dry with
OL,8,Fsome sunshine, reaching Wales and the
OL,9,Fnorth and west of England later.
OL,10,FGenerally cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
